{"tid":374372,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"CSS font-family問題","createTime":"2017-08-25T16:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T00:10:48.000Z","uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e7abd85d26af9415ca9dde2f58c71166e7a8cc7","tid":374372,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:31:44.000Z","msg":"我起緊個website，中文(字體A)同埋英文(字體B)都係分別用唔同既font<br />\n咁本身 字體A 入面就包中同英<br />\n<br />\n咁好自然font-family就set 字體B行先，之後先到字體A<br />\n咁我用Mac開都冇事 好正常<br />\n但當我去用windows開個website既時候，個字體B就唔work<br />\nwebsite入面既中英文都用左字體A<br />\n<br />\n兩隻字體我都用左font-face<br />\n呢個情況可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc626e3d4dabac14254ac6cf78c2fd6e3cf0bc6","tid":374372,"uid":51080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"冇code 睇叫人點答你？"},{"pid":"8719dab89da55897e8e6b0ffb661373117cbf758","tid":374372,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇code 睇叫人點答你？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/004013_59b234b265bb8174da3bc233b4bc81a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F004013_59b234b265bb8174da3bc233b4bc81a0.png&h=f4fc1180&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a755d9b25e12fc891cbccdd65bdfd569862a1c9d","tid":374372,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:40:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇code 睇叫人點答你？</blockquote><br />\nSorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3d7a48c3edef226219003ea8324eb1864ba6a3","tid":374372,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T19:40:48.000Z","msg":"unicode-range"},{"pid":"bc45b64c7afe922fadd57888f049d97affdf6561","tid":374372,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:08:26.000Z","msg":"1. Order from Specific (cjk) to general (Latin)<br />\n2. Consider using a Unicode font <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/get/noto/help/cjk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fget%2Fnoto%2Fhelp%2Fcjk%2F&d=7%2BaaaxUrS%2Fp8pEpoLvQwP0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e7336f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/get/noto/help/cjk/</a><br />\n3. Specific fallback. Go to site with working CSS font order and learn from it. Include both windows and Mac fonts as well as generic font family name such as serif etc"},{"pid":"a85f71c58ae284d75c2afb625af08c69c45c770b","tid":374372,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. Order from Specific (cjk) to general (Latin)<br />\n2. Consider using a Unicode font <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/get/noto/help/cjk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fget%2Fnoto%2Fhelp%2Fcjk%2F&d=7%2BaaaxUrS%2Fp8pEpoLvQwP0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e7336f13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/get/noto/help/cjk/</a><br />\n3. Specific fallback. Go to site with working CSS font order and learn from it. Include both windows and Mac fonts as well as generic font family name such as serif etc</blockquote><br />\nSorry 1 should be the other way around. My bad. <br />\n<br />\nSee the link here<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/get/noto/help/guidelines/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fget%2Fnoto%2Fhelp%2Fguidelines%2F&d=7%2BaaaxUrS%2Fp8pEpoLvQwP0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=b57ba0e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/get/noto/help/guidelines/</a>"}]}